Package: ezmmek
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Enzyme Activities on Synthetic Substrates using Michaelis-Menton Kinetics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher L. Cook and Andrew D. Steen
Maintainer: Christopher L. Cook <ccook62@vols.utk.edu>
Description: Analysis of enzyme activities on fluorogenic and chromogenic substrates using Michaelis-Menton kinetics. It outputs plots and relevant statistics regarding standard curves and saturation curves. It also enables the user to customize plots to their particular datasets.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    assertable,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    magrittr,
    nls2,
    purrr,
    scales,
    tidyr
Depends: R(>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat
